<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Stab1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Stab,</orth> subst. a thrust with the sharp point of a weapon: <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.3.63" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. III, 3, 63</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.119" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 119</bibl>. In a moral sense: <cit><quote>this sudden s. of rancour,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 3.2.89" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 2, 89</bibl></cit>.
